headline: 3 of the Best Growth Stocks You Can Buy for Less than $100
summary: It's getting harder these days to find great growth stocks trading for less than $100 a share.  Just remember that doing so means buying in when there may still be some price volatility and risk involved.  If you're looking at investments priced at less than $100, then three of the best growth stocks to consider right now are CRISPR Therapeutics (NASDAQ: CRSP), Celsius (NASDAQ: CELH), and KB Home (NYSE: KBH).
